arStrings.szText: “Zir’s forces have been routed. The survivors are safe.”
Yes, I saw it myself. (sigh) I once guessed your curse might be used to our advantage, but the way you tore through those Seekers...
Still processing what they saw. Amazed/frightened by Player's power.
You're ready to face Zir, and I’ve discovered how to open his gate. I'll ride for the City of the Ancients at once. Meet me there.
Refocusing. Terse. Bracing. Zir is pronounced (zeer).
